description: Navigate to Chinatown Gate. Follow Surface Road southwest, keeping the tree-lined greenway on the left and buildings on the right. Turn right at the intersection onto a paved plaza area featuring a mural. The route ends at a street corner marked by a red fence and Chinese restaurant signage, though the Chinatown Gate structure itself is not visible.
agent_refined_route: Head southwest on Surface Rd [137m] -> Turn right [34m]
